<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-content">
    <span class="hero-badge" data-en="Cleantech Innovation" data-lv="Tīro tehnoloģiju inovācija">
      Cleantech Innovation
    </span>
    <h1 class="hero-title">
      <span data-en="Alternative Fuel" data-lv="Alternatīvā Degviela">Alternative Fuel</span><br />
      <span data-en="Solutions for" data-lv="Risinājumi">Solutions for</span><br />
      <em data-en="Low-Emission Mobility" data-lv="Zemu Emisiju Mobilitātei">Low-Emission Mobility</em>
    </h1>
    <p
      class="hero-subtitle"
      data-en="ArtuPower enables diesel engines to run on cleaner alkane gas blends — reducing diesel consumption by up to 50% without replacing your existing fleet."
      data-lv="ArtuPower ļauj dīzeļdzinējiem darboties ar tīrākām alkāna gāzes maisījumiem — samazinot dīzeļa patēriņu par līdz 50%, neaizstājot esošo autoparka tehniku."
    >
      ArtuPower enables diesel engines to run on cleaner alkane gas blends — reducing diesel consumption by up to 50% without replacing your existing fleet.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a href="#products"  class="btn-primary" data-en="Explore Products" data-lv="Apskatīt Produktus">Explore Products</a>
      <a href="#mission"   class="btn-outline"  data-en="Watch Video"      data-lv="Skatīt Video">Watch Video</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.hero {
  position: relative; min-height: 100vh;
  background: url('https://www.artupower.eu/wp-content/uploads/hero-1.jpg') center / cover no-repeat;
  display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center;
}
.hero::after {
  content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0;
  background: linear-gradient(
    120deg,
    rgba(13,27,42,0.85) 0%,
    rgba(13,27,42,0.50) 55%,
    rgba(13,27,42,0.12) 100%
  );
}
.hero-content {
  position: relative; z-index: 1;
  padding: 130px 40px 60px;
  max-width: 740px;
}
.hero-badge {
  display: inline-block;
  background: var(--blue); color: #fff;
  font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase;
  padding: 5px 14px; border-radius: 3px; margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.hero-title {
  font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.6rem);
  font-weight: 800; color: #fff;
  line-height: 1.1; text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: -0.01em; margin-bottom: 22px;
}
.hero-title em { color: var(--blue); font-style: normal; }
.hero-subtitle {
  font-size: 1.05rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.82);
  line-height: 1.72; margin-bottom: 36px; max-width: 540px;
}
.hero-actions { display: flex; gap: 14px; flex-wrap: wrap; }

@media (max-width: 600px) {
  .hero-content { padding: 110px 20px 40px; }
}
</style>
